<html>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css"/>
	<head>
		<title>[7Pictures] 구매 취소 - <%= Title %> : <%= result_description %> </title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="mail-body">
			<div class="mail-logo-body">
				<img class="mail-logo" src="https://netflix-salon.co.kr/assets/images/7pictures_mail.jpg" > 
			</div>
			<div class="mail-content-body">
				<div class="mail-content-title">[구매 취소]</div>
				<div class="mail-content-text">안녕하세요, <%= address.addressee_name %>님!</div>
				<div class="mail-content-text">7Pictures 상점 구매가 취소 되었습니다.</div>
				<div class="mail-content-empty"></div>
				<h3>취소 내역</h3>
				<div class="mail-content-text">
					상 점 : <a href="<%= Link %>"> <%= Title %> </a>
				</div>
				<div class="mail-content-text">
					품 명 : <%= result_description %>
				</div>
				<div class="mail-content-text">
					금 액 : <%= amount %>원
				</div>
				<div class="mail-content-empty"></div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</body>
</html>
